index.html.title: darkFX - A dark theme for DocFX! | darkFX
index.html.keywords: darkFX - A dark theme for DocFX! A dark template for documentation generated with DocFX . This is an override of the default template so you need to enable both in the docfx.json . Install Download the source or the zipped file from the releases . Create a templates folder in the root of your DocFX directory. Copy the darkfx folder to the templates folder. Update the docfx.json configuration to include the material template: json { "template": [ "default", "templates/darkfx" ], } Acknowledgement Many thanks to Oscar VÃ¡squez from which I borrowed the example pages and repository structure of his Material Theme for DocFX .
